{"tid":1306022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武者，止戈也。","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T06:25:17.000Z","uid":76332,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0eb31f58fb374c6f535e6a0d9dae7dab58d393","tid":1306022,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"比到踩到上心口嘅時侯 用武力去制止係應該要做嘅事 你唔制止 只會助長暴力<br />\n<br />\n本身已經好嬲 但知道藍衫巴打原來有學武術之後 就更加嬲 <br />\n<br />\n我冇學過都知 武術係學嚟阻止暴力 呢樣係最根本嘅武德<br />\n<br />\n冇錯 兄弟爬山 各自努力 但而家有咁多人陪你癲 比人打到暈都仲咬住個光環 你又點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再講多一次 唔係要還手 係要制止</span></span>"},{"pid":"71e5ff4f56f04decaf63fd5dd861f88ab0b8fe3c","tid":1306022,"uid":76332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:12:57.000Z","msg":"醒未？"},{"pid":"f7aa8860ff25c018099d512b2961ff7d773185b2","tid":1306022,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa25d4fabe4dc86c66174b8830d2f64c6b0d8c7","tid":1306022,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"係咪仲要咬住光環唔放？"},{"pid":"c6dc00234d559f76f5f7bfe841fb931048186b85","tid":1306022,"uid":76332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff68120bfff9552b6e1d74763add1cc10eea4e7","tid":1306022,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兒登仔J緊話沙包男受過舞術訓練喎...<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母！乜嘢舞術訓練喺教人打不還手？<br />\n<br />\n柔道喺不傷對手的情況下壓制對方, 但不是打不還手！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兒登仔：依家喺「和理非回合」，點解我和理非都要打我？乜和